entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, it was great. Until the cops grabbed him.
Seriously. We were just sitting there at our table, eating, when suddenly they barge in, cuff him and drag him off.
I dunno. It's a first date, it's not, like, I'm gonna be, like, "Hey, by the way, are the cops after you?"
Yeah, yeah, Martha. Yeah, maybe I should.
Course I'm gonna call him. I had to pay for dinner, the gonk owes me.
